The aforementioned tissue-specific studies motivated a more thorough investigation about the relations between mutational profiles across cancer types and various normal tissue features. For each gene, we constructed a vector of mutational profile over available cancer types, where each component indicates its mutation frequency \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
